<br>
When you have 20 or 30 melee, all with a decent upgrade in damage, or defense, or whatever, it will start to make a difference in what those 20 or 30 people can do. Things like MGB also cut down on buffing times. Less time spent buffing = more time spent killing, generally.<br>
<br>
It's not really making everything ridiculously easy, so much as it is just making some things a little more plausible and doable.<br>
